  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA62">
<l>pēṟoṉṟu muṉṉaṟiyēṉ peṟṟaṟiyēṉ pētamaiyāṉ</l>
<l>māṟeṉṟu colli vaṇaṅkiṉē – ṉēṟiṉ</l>
<l>perutteruttaṅ kōṭociyap peṇṇacaiyiṉ piṉpō</l>
<l>yeruttiṟutta nallāya rēṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, who before did not know any goal, who out of foolishness did not know of obtaining [it], I bowed,</l>
<l>saying ‘change’ – before the bull among good cowherds</l>
<l>who, going after the woman out of desire, when he twisted [its] neck</l>
<l>by the horns, broke the bull’s neck.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
